{"tid":1175361,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[藝用人體學] 到底動漫有咩係唔合理？","createTime":"2019-05-28T13:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T03:42:13.000Z","uid":198503,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d2129a7eb6cd1e2442de9be7c21c16e3e6422a08","tid":1175361,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:20:34.000Z","msg":"歡迎post圖問問題<br />\n拋豬引肉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上唔寫實嘅我都敢講人體唔會準得去邊<br />\n唔係嘅話喺製作上好多難題<br />\n<br />\n你可以話喺畫畫風格唔同<br />\n但係改變唔到&rsquo;&rsquo;畫出嚟有問題&rsquo;&rsquo;嘅呢個結果<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.hypebeast.com/files/2019/03/dragon-ball-super-broly-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.hypebeast.com%2Ffiles%2F2019%2F03%2Fdragon-ball-super-broly-3.jpg&h=13e6c311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幅可以見到鳥山明係簡化左人體，尤其喺呢啲大隻到唔合理嘅角色上<br />\n而其中一邊乳頭係錯左perspective <br />\n<br />\n喺人體學其中一樣比較困難係要想像邊啲肌肉會變得極發達<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.comicbook.com/2019/02/gogeta-dragon-ball-super-broly-1159893-1280x0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.comicbook.com%2F2019%2F02%2Fgogeta-dragon-ball-super-broly-1159893-1280x0.jpeg&h=1fa11453&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無可否認畫出嚟係好睇<br />\n好多人會問，佢頭蓋骨會係咩樣?<br />\n其實答案大家都知<br />\n好多唔寫實嘅公仔基本上係有design 而無 mechanics<br />\n譬如賽路路畫風，對眼大到cls<br />\n但係有個中心方向，就係順眼就得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只係呢啲風格對於某啲傳統學院派畫家嚟講係唔太接受到<br />\n甚至有人話日本公仔根本唔係藝術<br />\n咁我自己係有保留啦<br />\n<br />\n我本人就最鍾意vagabond嘅作者"},{"pid":"689107d94a7c3f14a28255e7b8c0ee4ee891b092","tid":1175361,"uid":7840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:32:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"88e259f00391d316f5eeba2e41d605e0cfaacc7b","tid":1175361,"uid":198503,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"689107d94a7c3f14a28255e7b8c0ee4ee891b092","tid":1175361,"uid":7840,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T13:32:31.000Z","msg"